elements.name: Hire budget SUV with five seats for one week trip

steps.name: user is on budget application home page
user types "aus" and selects pickup and return location as "Austin Bergstrom Intl Airport"
pickup date as week ahead of current date
return date as week ahead of pickup date
clicks Select My car option to navigate to reservations page
chooses lowest price SUV with "4" doors and "5" seats and click pay now option
user validates base rate, fees and taxes and estimated prepaid total succesfully
